name: The Doge Overlord Recurring
description: Doge Overlord, has pierced the membrane of reality and now his inner Doge is opening his third eye wide open, who is in turn having his third opened by an inner inner Doge, and so on...... This is a remix version by Artserge - @msergisonmain of an original artwork by Cryptowook | cryptowook.xyz | Twitter: @crypto_wook
